Setswana: Ditlhaketlhake tsa Borwa jwa Shetland, bo lemogilwe ka 1819, bontsi jwa ditšhaba tse di farologaneng bo ile jwa re bolela fa ele ditlhaketlhake jwa tsone le gore di na le motheo o montsi, tse lesome le borataro ka 2020. 
English: South Shetland Islands, discovered in 1819, are claimed by several nations and have the most bases, with sixteen active in 2020.
clean_output: South Shetland Islands, discovered in 1819, are claimed by several nations and have the most bases, with sixteen active in 2020.

text: Apia ke motsemoshate wa Samoa. Toropo eno e mo setlhaketlhakeng sa Upolu mme e na le baagi ba ba kwa tlasenyana fela ga 40,000.
translated_text:
Setswana: Apia ke motsemoshate wa Samoa. Toropo eno e mo setlhaketlhakeng sa Upolu mme e na le baagi ba ba kwa tlasenyana fela ga 40,000. 
English: Capital: Apia is the capital of Samoa. The city is on the island of Upolu and has a population of just under 40,000.
clean_output: Capital: Apia is the capital of Samoa. The city is on the island of Upolu and has a population of just under 40,000.

text: E re ka setsuatsue se le kgakala le go goroga mo lefatsheng, ga go bonolo go ka sekaseka go re ditlamorago tsa sone di tla nna jang mo lefatsheng la Amerika kgotsa kwa Caribbean.
translated_text:
Setswana: E re ka setsuatsue se le kgakala le go goroga mo lefatsheng, ga go bonolo go ka sekaseka go re ditlamorago tsa sone di tla nna jang mo lefatsheng la Amerika kgotsa kwa Caribbean. 
English: As the storm is far from landfall, it is difficult to assess potential impact to the United States or Caribbean.
clean_output: As the storm is far from landfall, it is difficult to assess potential impact to the United States or Caribbean.

text: Le le sesane fa tlase ga mawatle, la bo le nna lekimanyana fa tlase ga dithota.
translated_text:
Setswana: Le le sesane fa tlase ga mawatle, la bo le nna lekimanyana fa tlase ga dithota. 
English: It is thinner under the maria and thicker under the highlands.
clean_output: It is thinner under the maria and thicker under the highlands.

text: Dikgwa tse ga se mafelo a loraga a a tletseng metsi fela, go na le mafelo a kileng a bo a aperwe ke dikgwa tse di tona tse di kitlameng, tse di tala.
translated_text:
Setswana: Dikgwa tse ga se mafelo a loraga a a tletseng metsi fela, go na le mafelo a kileng a bo a aperwe ke dikgwa tse di tona tse di kitlameng, tse di tala. 
English: Canyons: Canyons are not just dry, rocky areas with a deep bottom.
clean_output: Canyons: Canyons are not just dry, rocky areas with a deep bottom.

text: Mmepe wa mafatshefatshe ka thoromo ya lefatshe ka ba lephata la badupi ba tshekatsheko ya popego ya lefatshe ke ba United States, o supile go re ga go a nna le thoromo ya lefatshe mo Iceland beke pele ga moo.
translated_text:
Setswana: Mmepe wa mafatshefatshe ka thoromo ya lefatshe ka ba lephata la badupi ba tshekatsheko ya popego ya lefatshe ke ba United States, o supile go re ga go a nna le thoromo ya lefatshe mo Iceland beke pele ga moo. 
English: The United States Geological Survey international earthquake map showed no earthquakes in Iceland in the week prior.
clean_output: The United States Geological Survey international earthquake map showed no earthquakes in Iceland in the week prior.

text: Ke iketlile mo godimo ga nngwe ya dithaba kwa Bokone jwa Mecca, logaga lono lo ikemetse kwa thoko fela lo le nosi mo lefatsheng lotlhe.
translated_text:

English: Mountain: Mountain is one of the highest mountains in the world, located in the north of the holy city of Mecca.
clean_output: Mountain: Mountain is one of the highest mountains in the world, located in the north of the holy city of Mecca.
